---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
const pageTitle = "tapasrm";
---

<Layout pageTitle={pageTitle}>
  <div class="gif">
    <img width="300" height="259" alt="RaccoonSpaceGif" src="/space.webp" />
  </div>
  <h1>Tapas Mohanta</h1>
  <small>Digital Craftsman (Developer)</small>
  <h2>About</h2>
  <p>
    I'm a Systems Developer who's all about crafting efficient solutions.
    Currently, I work as a Backend Web Developer at Brillio Technologies Pvt
    Ltd. My programming journey started back in high school and hasn't stopped
    since. Whether it's containers, VMs, on-premises setups, or even a Raspberry
    Pi, I thrive on making things work seamlessly across different platforms.
    Let's bring ideas to life!

    <p>
      I've worked on many cool projects both at my work and my free time. I
      share some of those work and ideas over at my blog. Be aware that I can be
      very opinionated sometimes.
    </p>
    <div class="button">
      <a href="/works/">
        <button>My portfolio</button>
      </a>
    </div>
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="link-images">
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="TypeScript"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/typescript/typescript-plain.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="NodeJS"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/nodejs/nodejs-plain.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Express"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/express/express-original.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Rust"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/rust/rust-plain.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Docker"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/docker/docker-original.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Nginx"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/nginx/nginx-original.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="PostgreSQL"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/postgresql/postgresql-original.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Linux"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/linux/linux-original.svg"
      />
      <img
        width="46"
        height="46"
        alt="Algorithms"
        src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/devicons/devicon/icons/thealgorithms/thealgorithms-plain.svg"
      />
    </div>
    <h2>Interests</h2>
    <p>
      I Love photography and gaming in my free time. I also discovered
      Philosophy during the Lockdown and enjoy reading Greek and Modern
      Philosophy
    </p>
  </p>
  <style>
    /* small */
    small {
      background-color: #584966;
      color: #fdebf3;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-family: "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: 0.3em 0.6em 0.2em;
    }

    /* Button */
    button {
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);
      border: 2px solid #78c2ad;
      border-radius: 8px;
      color: #78c2ad;
      font: 600 16px "Josefin Sans", sans-serif;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      transition: background-color 0.4s, color 0.4s;
    }

    button:hover {
      background-color: #78c2ad;
      color: #fdebf3;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .button {
      text-align: center;
    }

    /* Skill images */
    .link-images img {
      margin: 16px 4px;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .link-images img {
        height: 30px;
        width: 30px;
        margin: 16px 1px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
